<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Usinipite! TZR10</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Usinipite Mwokozi,
 Unisikie;
 Unapozuru wengine,
 Usinipite.

[V2]
 Yesu,Yesu,
 Unisikie;
 Unapozuru wengine,
 Usinipite.

[V3]
 Kiti chako cha rehema,
 Nakitazama;
 Magoti napiga pale,
 Nisamehewe.

[V4]
 Sina ya kutegemea,
 Ila Wewe tu;
 Uso wako uwe kwangu;
 Nakuabudu.

[V5]
 U Mfariji peke yako;
 Sina Mbinguni,
 Wala duniani pote,
 Bwana mwingine.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>10</hymn_number>
</song>